quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  40,38,"Naho wawundi wemeye (wo mu bantu ba Farawo) aravuga ati \"Yemwe bantu banjye! Nimunkurikire mbayobore mu nzira itunganye"
  40,39,"Yemwe bantu banjye! Mu by’ukuri, ubu buzima bw’isi ni umunezero w’igihe gito, kandi rwose (ubuzima bw’) imperuka ni bwo buturo buzahoraho"
  40,40,"Uzakora igikorwa kibi azahembwa ikingana nacyo, na ho uzakora igikorwa cyiza, yaba umugabo cyangwa umugore akaba ari n’umwemera; abo nibo bazinjira mu ijuru, bahabwe amafunguro nta kugera"
  40,41,"Yemwe bantu banjye! Kuki mbahamagarira kurokoka, mwe mukampamagarira kugana umuriro"
  40,42,"Murampamagarira guhakana Allah ngo mubangikanye n’ibyo ntafitiye ubumenyi? Nyamara njye ndabahamagarira kugana (Allah) Nyir’imbaraga zihebuje, Ubabarira ibyaha"
  40,43,"Nta kabuza ko ibyo mumpamagarira ntacyo byamarira mu byo nabisaba, haba ku isi cyangwa ku mperuka, kandi igarukiro ryacu ni kwa Allah. Kandi abarengera imbago (za Allah) ni bo bantu bo mu muriro"
  40,44,"Kandi muzibuka ibyo mbabwira! Nanjye ibyanjye mbyeguriye Allah! Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Ubona abagaragu be mu buryo buhebuje"
  40,45,"Nuko Allah amurinda imigambi mibisha yabo bari bagambiriye, maze ibihano bibi bigera ku bantu ba Farawo"
  40,46,"Umuriro bawushyirwamo mu gitondo na nimunsi (aho bari mu mva zabo), n’igihe umunsi w’imperuka wageze (abamalayika bazabwirwa bati): \"Nimwinjize abantu ba Farawo mu bihano (umuriro) bibabaza cyane"
  40,47,"Kandi zirikana ubwo bazatongana bari mu muriro baterana amagambo, maze abanyantegenke babwire babandi bibonaga (ku isi) bati \"Mu by’ukuri, ni mwe twakurikiraga. Ese none hari icyo mwatumarira, mu kutugabanyiriza kuri ibi bihano by’umuriro"
  40,48,"Babandi bibonaga (ku isi) bazavuga bati \"Rwose twese tuwurimo! Mu by’ukuri, Allah yamaze gukiranura abagaragu be"
  40,49,"Nuko abari mu muriro bazabwire abarinzi ba Jahanamu bati \"Nimudusabire Nyagasani wanyu atugabanyirize ibihano kabone n’ubwo byaba umunsi umwe"
  40,50,"(Bazababwira bati \"Ese intumwa zanyu ntizabageragaho zibazaniye ibimenyetso bigaragara?\" Bavuge bati \"Nibyo b’umuriro) (zatugezeho)!\" bavuge bati (Abarinzi \"Ngaho nimusabe ariko ugusaba kw’abahakanyi ntacyo kumara uretse igihombo)"